Class AuthenticatingHttpProxy

java.lang.Object
  org.aludratest.service.gui.web.selenium.httpproxy.AuthenticatingHttpProxy

public class AuthenticatingHttpProxy
extends Object

Opens a server socket at the localPort, receives HTTP requests, injects custom HTTP request headers and forwards the request to the server realHost.

setCustomRequestHeader

public void setCustomRequestHeader(String key,
                                   String value)
Sets the name-value pair of a custom HTTP request header to add to forwarded calls. For each request header to be set, all incoming request headers of the same key are deleted, then the new value is set.
